  <Placemark>
   <name>Gale Warning issued October 11 at 2:45PM EDT until October 12 at 11:00PM EDT by NWS Newport/Morehead City NC</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_moderate</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northeast winds 25 to 35 kt with gusts up to 45 kt and
seas 12 to 17 ft expected.

* WHERE...The coastal waters from Oregon Inlet to Ocracoke Inlet.

* WHEN...Until 11 PM EDT Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.</Snippet>
