  <Placemark>
   <name>Small Craft Advisory issued October 11 at 11:13AM PDT until October 14 at 11:00PM PDT by NWS Medford OR</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...North winds 10 to 20 kt with occasional gusts to 25 kt
and seas 8 to 11 ft at 10 seconds expected.

* WHERE...All areas, except strongest winds and highest seas will
be beyond 20 NM from shore.

* WHEN...From 8 PM this evening to 11 PM PDT Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds and/or steep seas could capsize or
damage smaller vessels.

* View the hazard area in detail at https://go.usa.gov/x6hks</Snippet>
   <ExtendedData>
    <Data name="ext_event">
     <value>Small Craft Advisory</value>
    </Data>
    <Data name="ext_severity">
     <value>Minor</value>
