   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northeast winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt.
Waves of 3 to 5 feet in sounds and seas 5 to 8 ft in the open
Gulf waters.

* WHERE...Sounds and open Gulf waters.

* WHEN...Until 7 PM CDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.</Snippet>
