   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>At 1030 AM AST, Doppler radar indicated strong thunderstorms,
capable of producing winds to around 30 knots. These thunderstorms
were located along a line extending from the offshore Caribbean
waters to over and north of St. Thomas. The thunderstorms were
nearly stationary.</Snippet>
