   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...For the Small Craft Advisory, seas 7 to 10 ft at 11
seconds and northwest winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt
expected. For the Hazardous Seas Watch, very steep and hazardous
seas 9 to 13 ft at 12 seconds and northwest winds 10 to 20 kt
with gusts up to 25 kt possible.

* WHERE...Inner Coastal Waters from Cape Shoalwater to Florence
out 10 NM, Waters from Cape Falcon to Cape Foulweather OR from
10 to 60 NM, and Waters from Cape Foulweather to Florence OR
from 10 to 60 NM.

* WHEN...Small Craft Advisory, from 3 PM this afternoon to 11 PM
PDT this evening. Hazardous Seas Watch, from this evening
through Sunday afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Very steep and hazardous seas could capsize or cause
damage to vessels.</Snippet>
