   <Snippet>* WHAT...Northeast winds 25 to 35 kt with gusts potentially up to
50 kt and seas 6 to 9 feet possible across the Long Island
Sound.

* WHERE...Long Island Sound, Peconic and Gardiners Bays, and
South Shore Bays from Jones Inlet through Shinnecock Bay.

* WHEN...From Sunday morning through Monday afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Storm force winds and hazardous seas could capsize
or damage vessels and reduce visibility.</Snippet>
