   <Snippet>* WHAT...For the Small Craft Advisory, east winds 20 to 30 kt
with gusts up to 35 kt and seas 6 to 9 feet expected. For the
Storm Warning, northeast winds 30 to 40 kt with gusts up to 50
kt and seas 14 to 19 feet expected.

